==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*γάρ: /gɑɹ/

===Conjunction===
*for, since, then, indeed, certainly
*Used as marker of cause/reason, to correlate multiple arguments for the same idea, or for emphasis or clarification.

===Placement===
γάρ is a post-positive word, i.e. it is never the first word in a sentence.  It is usually the second, but sometimes also the third or fourth.